From ec83629b678483c0c5beea4f598f99d5afc0f986 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Sushant Butta <sbutta@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Tue, 1 Jul 2025 00:18:38 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 3/6] UPSTREAM: DP: wifi: ath12k: Refactor WCN7850 Status Ring
 Handling to dp_mon1.c

WCN7850 status ring processing is currently part of ath12k/dp_mon.c
(ath12k.ko common module) with the Unified Driver framework,
WCN7850 adopts the monitor quad ring model (mon1), so the status ring
processing logic is being moved to the architecture-specific file
ath12k/wifi7/dp_mon1.c(ath12k_wifi7.ko arch specific module)

Patch-dependency:
	0404-0002-UPSTREAM-DP-wifi-ath12k-Segregate-Architecture-Speci.patch

Signed-off-by: Sushant Butta <sbutta@qti.qualcomm.com>
